{
  "id": "adv_event_2209_01_02",
  "title": "未来とつながるマジカルメロディ 2話 ミクの記念日",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "初めまして、初音ミクです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hi‚ I'm Hatsune Miku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEのみんな、よろしくね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you all‚ TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "凄い……これ、ホログラムって技術ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing… Is this hologram technology?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、顔合わせが出来てる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can meet like this..wow….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私からも、みんなのこと、ちゃんと見えてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can see everyone properly from my side too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "天動瑠依ちゃん、鈴村優ちゃん、奥山すみれちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui Tendo-chan‚ Yu Suzumura-chan‚ Sumire Okuyama-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うっ！　本物のミクちゃんから名前呼ばれた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh! Being called by the real Miku-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うち、幸せ者過ぎるやろ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so lucky…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こちらこそ初めまして、ミクちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you too‚ Miku-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、凄い機械だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is an amazing machine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "普段、初音さんがライブステージに立つ時も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally‚ when Hatsune-san performs on the live stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "同じような原理の機械を使ってるそうだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They use a similar principle with the machine‚ I heard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "呼ぶ時はミクでいいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can call me Miku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3417031606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか。分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Okay‚ got it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私はネットワークの世界に生きてるからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I live in the network world‚ you see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "いろんなデバイスを、自由に行き来出来るんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can freely move between various devices.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから、バーチャル・シンガーっていうんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why they call youo a virtual singer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……やっぱり触れられないのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… still can't be physically touched.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3131266911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あくまでも投影されてる状態やからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ she is just being projected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、こうしてお話し出来るだけでも十分やんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But being able to have this conversation is already enough‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "歌を届けるのに、必ずしも体は必要じゃないからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't necessarily need a physical body to deliver my songs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "今のままでも、出来ることは沢山あるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even in this form‚ there are plenty of things I can do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なるほど、そうかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might be true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……改めてよろしくね、ミク",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Nice to meet you again‚ Miku!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さて。この前も伝えたけど、トリエルの三人には",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then. As I mentioned before‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "マジカルミライに出演してもらう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE is going to perform at Magical Mirai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ミクちゃんのライブに出演かぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To perform at Miku-chan's live. It's both exciting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと観る側やったから、嬉しいし感慨深いわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and emotional for me‚ since I've always been on the watching side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "改めて、出演を決めてくれてありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you once again for deciding to perform!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが出演してくれたら、絶対素敵なライブになるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It will be a fantastic concert with everyone's participation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ミクちゃんからのオファーだもん、断れないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can't refuse an offer from Miku-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "お祝いの気持ち、いーっぱい届けるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll express lots of celebration and support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "曲構成はどうするん？　うちらの既存曲を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about the song arrangement?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ歌うだけなんは、なんや申し訳ないなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels a bit inadequate if we just sing our existing songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ミクの曲をカバーしたり、でしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are we going to cover Miku's songs‚ perhaps?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、対応は可能ですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ we can do that…But..",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いや、今回は新曲をつくろうと思ってるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ this time I'm thinking of creating a new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1,
      "sfxList": []
